title: Exceptional Lease with Right to Purchase Opportunity
posting_body: ['Contact me to learn more about an innovative Lease with Right to Purchase program.', 'Unlike many rent to own programs or lease options, there is no obligation to buy and no non-refundable option fees.', 'Basic Requirements to Qualify**:', '• Annual household income of $50,000+', '• Stable employment', '• No history of eviction or other landlord issues • No pending bankruptcy', '• No disqualifying criminal history', 'Contact me today for more information.', 'If you are interested in applying for the program, feel free to visit my website <URL> and look under the resources tab along top of site and scroll down to the link that says HomePartners once you click that link you should be able to click the apply now link and complete registration.', 'Please make sure it says Andre Jones as your real estate agent before proceeding', 'I look forward to working with you to place you and your family in the home you deserve!!!', "Andre' Jones", 'Managing Real Estate Broker', 'Skyline Properties, Inc – Puyallup Branch', '702 S. Hill Park Rd, Suite 203', 'Puyallup, WA 98373', 'show contact info', 'Cell', 'show contact info', 'Fax']
